; ITERATIVE FIBONACCI, SHOWING TYPED LOCALS, ASSIGNMENT, AND A `&` LOOP.
; LOCALS ARE DECLARED `!NAME TYPE`; ASSIGNMENT IS POSTFIX `VALUE NAME!`.

!FIB W, N W
    !A W
    !B W
    !T W
    !I W
    0 A!
    1 B!
    0 I!
    I N < &
        A B + T!
        B A!
        T B!
        I 1 + I!
    A @

!MAIN W
    !I W
    0 I!
    I 10 < &
        I FIB PRINT
        I 1 + I!
